sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

User->>Frontend: View room schedule
Frontend->>API: GET /api/rooms/:roomId/schedule
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: parsePositiveInt(roomId)
alt Invalid room id
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid room id
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Valid room id
API->>API: Validate start_time/end_time or compute range
alt Only one of start_time/end_time provided
API-->>Frontend: 400 Both start_time and end_time are required together
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Both provided or computed
alt Invalid start_time or end_time format
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid start_time or end_time format
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Range determined
alt end_time <= start_time
API-->>Frontend: 400 end_time must be greater than start_time
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Range valid
API->>DB: Query room by id
alt Room not found
DB-->>API: empty
API-->>Frontend: 404 Room not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Room found
API->>DB: Query bookings in range
DB-->>API: booking rows
API-->>Frontend: 200 schedule payload
Frontend-->>User: Render schedule
end
end
end
end
end
end
